    dc:title "A new genus of Eurrhacini from the Brazilian Atlantic Forest (Coleoptera: Lycidae: Lycinae) with an updated key to genera" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10351320>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10351324>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10351326> ;
